Title: Blade of the General
Description:
Even now, General Anub'azal's forces work tirelessly to ensure the security of Azj-Kahet.

Ansurek's reach extends to every corner of her domain. The General seeks to undermine her military authority. If we stretch her resources thin, then we may find new opportunities to strike.
ObjectivesText: Continue your efforts in aiding the General in Azj-Kahet.

Objectives.Text: View Yamas the Provider's Pact items
